conqueror is the weakest rune - meaning that even conqueror users are better off with press the attack,comet,grasp of the undying except for few exceptions {{champion:122}} {{champion:24}} {{champion:11}} 

the rune is band aid for bruisers - without conqueror top lane was dominated by tanks. With conqueror top lane roster grew to roughly 2,5x the size than before. With conqueror and without tanks, much more champions are viable other than tank busters. 

Honestly all conqueror does is remove tanks from the game which is statistically not bad in any sense other than giving autofills braindead champions to play and win lane againist someone who mains bruisers. If you wanna win on top lane, its time to start actually playing top lane.
